Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can tell me what these are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Various] Treasure?\NShiny! Me likey. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all legendary\Nmagical artifacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.  I read ahead in Equestrian\NCultures and Camaraderie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Ocellus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Amulet of Aurora,\Nthe Talisman of Mirage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the Helm of Yksler,\Nthe Crown of Grover,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Knuckerbocker's Shell and\NClover the Clever's Cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the gems are real!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. not that I tasted them..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia gifted\Nthese to our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,since they each represent\None of the cultures
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,our students come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll learn all about them\Nwith a Spell-venger hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a pony thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Meh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a magical\Nscavenger hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of you will work\Nin pairs to try to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,where in the school these\Nartifacts are hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The team that finds the most\Nwins a private tour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Canterlot archives\Nwith Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Learning AND fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it get any\Nbetter than that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been underwater a\N{\i1}long{\i0} time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Gallus and Silverstream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're\Nour first pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They'll make\Na great team!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Why pony glowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you all were called on\Nthis friendship quest, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a {\i1}really{\i0}\Nimportant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And terribly\Nfar away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Just getting there\Nwill take DAYS!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do y'all know\Nwhat this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any teachers\Nleft to run the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we send\Nour students home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we take\N'em with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ROAD TRIP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of my\Nfriendship quilting class?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those\Nunfinished seams....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem is, we don't even\Nknow how long we'll be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Don't worry, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have a\Nseventy-point plan in place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for this very situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You want ME to be Headmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the\Nperfect choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good leader,\Nand an expert in\Nfriendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you to run this\Nschool exactly as I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's a pretty big\Nresponsibility, Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I've prepared\Neverything you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The curriculum, rules\Nfor the Spellvenger hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,dining hall menus for\Nthe next six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Six months!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really gonna be\Ngone that long, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that isn't\Ncovered in my files,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be able to\Nhelp you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not put\Nhim in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No-o-o, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a princess for\NTwilight was hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pretend\Nthat made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're sure it's\Nwhat you really want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[rustling]\NGah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What could possibly go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate goodbyes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just go to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,nice surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your first time at\Nour new school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was I not invited\Nto the grand opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends and Family Day?\NBaccalaureate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All: I hadn't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least you're here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, why ARE you here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To fill in for\NTwilight, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As Headdraconequus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to recall a whole song\Nabout how this school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is where you make\Nyour own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who better at that than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you ALSO must've heard\NStarlight is in charge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I thought there\Nmust be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, Twilight picked\Nme for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And she left pretty detailed\Ninstructions for me to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure that\Nshe wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if I made a few\NTINY suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Item one, gravity is optional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Item two, the\Nschool's new mascot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is an ambidextrous marmoset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Item three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Twilight I'd\Nhandle this her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reeeeeeally?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see if\Nyou change your mind..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When we play Ogres\Nand Oubliettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and he puts that many\Neeeees in "really",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,things don't usually end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord and I are old\Nsave-Equestria buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's next\Non Twilight's list?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, I hid the artifacts\Nfor the Spellvenger hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and ordered school\Nsupplies for the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to worry\Nabout is teaching class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we will get\Nthrough this OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, come in, you'll\Nlet the twittermites out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Twittermites?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OW!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony was at\Nyour desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine what\NTwilight would say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How could\Nyou, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've broken my trust\Nand failed me completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry,\NI'll cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I hope you\Nlike Limburger cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a month's supply\Nfor the teacher's lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take it from\Nhere, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go relax, have a\Ncup of tea. At home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Some thanks for all my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I hired all those\Nsubstitute teachers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that does\Nsound kinda helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was next\Non our to do list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WHICH teachers did you hire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it making friends\Nbecause you have to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,MAKE creatures be\Nyour friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what\Nyou got, Yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're quiet, I don't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard pudding\Nthat's more convincing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,BE. MY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,FRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how Twilight\Nteaches friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Some field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's too TEA-FLAVORED!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourselves friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is definitely not how\NTwilight teaches friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You hired a TREE\Nas a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Its schedule was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Uh, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not\Njust any tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[blowing] It's a\NDragonsneeze tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait Wait! Calm down,\Nevery creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-YA!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,BE MY FRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My my my, you do seem like\Nyou're in over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't Twilight be\Nso disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,with how you're ruining, I\Nmean RUNNING her school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! This is\Nall your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine? I thought YOU\Nwere in charge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy to pitch\Nin if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need is\Nfor you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's\Nnot what she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I\Nwon't try to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,AT ALL!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope\Nhe stays gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Discord's\Ntrying to test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's kinda what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even to ponies or\Ndragons he cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I'm ready\Nfor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Twilight I'd\Nrun her school right,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna\Nkeep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight: Good morning, students!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's been a little\Nbit of adjustment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,since the Professors\Nleft for their trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've brought in\Nnew new teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and now everything\Nshould run smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, this afternoon\Nis the Spellvenger hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[door slams open]\N[startled gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Greetings, fellow creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this seat taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome class!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You may call me the Great and\NPowerful Professor Trrrr--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's so inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd better take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I'm a student of\Nfriendship, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you don't think you're\Ngood enough to teach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No fruit calls in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is the most important\Nelement of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So today, I, the Great and\NPowerful Trixie, will put on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A MAGIC SHOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh oh, I'm learning\NSO much, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,GRRRRRR...Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what exactly IS a\Nlong-distance plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a lap, team!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually, we just finished\NProfessor Spitfire's workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like somepony\Nneeds a little motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never run so\Nfast in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Hey, Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is about honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So believe me when I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona...can't run...faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Endangering students\Ncrosses the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're\Ntrying to ruin this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it stops now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your last warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's your friend, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's not acting like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the fact that Twilight\Ndecided to put an incompetent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,power-hungry unicorn in charge\Nof her school MY PROBLEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha hah.. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just banished him from\Nschool grounds forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That probably made\Nthings worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just\Ntalk to Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's right\Nabout one thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing a\Nterrible job as Headmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord is just\Nbeing... Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why me being in\Ncharge bothers him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can figure that out\NAFTER the Spellvenger Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For this afternoon's\NSpellvenger Hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll need to use the\Nartifacts' history
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to find where they're\Nhidden in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When you spot one, touch\Nit with a magic shield
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep track\Nof your score.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight left a list of your\Nhunt partners before she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass out the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, set... Spellvenger Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, we can use Twilight's\Nobservatory to watch the teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you know\Nwhere you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Helm of Yksler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In our book, it says Yksler\Nwas an honorable Yak warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Any enemies that saw him put\Ndown their weapons in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his artifact must be in\None of these suits of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! One down, five to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Ocellus and Smolder\Nfound their first artifact!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't think that's part\Nof the Spellvenger Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The school is haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally gonna win\Nthis Spellvenger Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least I know where\None of the artifacts is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw Spike hide it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crown of Grover!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's magic, and King\NGrover used it to become
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the first ruler of Griffonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, pretty sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You paid attention in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What! If you\Never tell an-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! 3-D painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's definitely Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you banished\Nhim from the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, his ghost can\Ncome and go just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, we have to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How? No offense, but\NI don't think magic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is the answer\Nagainst Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm not using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What Yona look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The shell of Knuckerbocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a seashell, but if you\Nblow into it, you call a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a sweet poem\Nin our book about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Climb to the heights with\Ndragon flight."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Like flight of stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona take pony word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yona not know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona DO know Yona not\Nlike Spellvenger Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho ho ho ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Boo Boo-boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oo! Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everycreature, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But-but-but the\Nschool is haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not haunted; it's Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Starlight!\NLook at me, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won the Spellvenger Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what's my prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, you can't keep\Nmessing up the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I think\NI rather can, and will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have just one\Nthing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop thinking like a\NHeadmare and start thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,like a Guidance Counselor\Nto finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...... I-I-I-I don't know what\Nyou're getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony ever invited\Nyou to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you offered to\Nhelp, I didn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried about doing\Nthings Twilight's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't stop to think\Nabout being a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And offer you the\Njob of vice-headmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I ACCEPT!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I.. I suppose I can find\Nsome time in my busy schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will need my own office,\Nexpense account, parking space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're new to the world\Nof education, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you want something,\Njust ask for it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But then we'd miss out on all\Nthese delightful misadventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch the wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, vice-headmare Discord,\Nif you'll help me get this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spellvenger Hunt back in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is re-hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Well, with\Na few surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,DISCORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you tricked us\Ninto going on a friendship quest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, back so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A glamour spell on\Nour cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake summons from the map?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at least we got\Nto go spelunking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in that really creepy\Ncave with all those
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,eyeless worm\Ncreatures chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yona so glad ponies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, y'all get the feelin'\Nwe missed something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking care\Nof the school, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think\Nthings turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just the way you'd\Nhave handled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this means you're\Nnot vice-headmare anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh poo! I just ordered\Nbusiness cards!
